item.description:
PreNorm Layer Custom layer representing the Pre-Normalization used within the transformer model. It takes the following parameter:
fn: The function to be applied to the normalized input. In the transformer, this function can be either the attention mechanism or the MLP. The call method is where the actual pre-normalization takes place. It takes the following parameters:
x: The input tensor passed through the layer normalization. training: Used to enable/disable dropout layers based on the training mode.
